resources.string:
Password recovery:
        \n - enter the phone number in the appropriate field, in the format: +7XXXXXXXXX, confirm the entry;
        \n - wait for an SMS message with a confirmation code (within a minute), enter the code in the appropriate field,
        confirm the entry;
        \n - if successful, a new password will be generated, which is required to enter the group, save it;
        \n - if the sms with the code did not come, click on the link \"Request SMS code again\", and repeat the steps
        from the first.
        \n\nTo return to the previous screen, select the Back arrow-shaped icon at the top of the application.
